# Config and Build Rules

- Only make explicitly requested changes; avoid unrelated edits
- Do not add dependencies or change formats unless explicitly allowed
- Assume API/ABI and data formats are stable; flag compatibility impacts
- Keep build artifacts out of the repo (respect `.gitignore`)
- Libraries in `lib/` are committed despite `.gitignore`
